        "subject": "=Project Timeline Revised: {{$json.project_title}}\n\n",
        "html": "=Dear {{$json.RecipientName}},\n\nPlease note that the project timeline for <b>{{$json.project_title}}</b> has been revised based on recent planning updates.\n\n<b>Updated Project Schedule</b>\n* Project Name: {{$json.project_title}}\n* Revised Start Date: {{$json.start_date}}\n* Revised End Date: {{$json.end_date}}\n* Revision Updated On: {{$json.updated_at}}\n\nThis change may affect task schedules, milestones, and resource planning. Team members are advised to review updated timelines and adjust their execution plans accordingly.\n\nRegards,\n<b>Project Controls & Planning Team</b>\n\n\n",
